HW04 Readme:

This application will load different types of paint on canvas
Comparing with last assignment, this time we the balls can interact with each other

Type the name of ball strategy into the text field on the left. 
Available strategies (* means it can interact with other balls):
1.Color
2.Breathing
3.Wander
4.Sleeping
5.Curve
6.Straight
*7. Average
*8. Blackhole
*9. Collide
*10. Eat
*11. Infect
*12. Kill
*13. Stop

Type the name of a paint strategy into the text field on the bottom. 
Available strategies:
1.Ball
2.Ellipse
3.Fish1
4.Fish2
5.NiceFish
6.PlanetImage
7.SharkImage
8.Square

First, Click the "Add paint" button, then add it to the paint drop lists.
"Make Switcher" will make a paint, initially, ones that go straight. 
Clicking the "Add strategy" button will then add it to both the drop lists.
"Make Ball" will make a ball with the strategy selected on the top drop list.
"Combine!" will dynamically create a strategy that is the combination of the strategies selected on top and bottom lists. 
The new strategy is placed back into both drop lists and can be used again for combining. 
For instance, add then combine "Curve" and "Breathing" to make a ball that curves and breathes.
Clicking "Switch!" will cause all Switcher balls ever made to switch behaviors to whatever is the selected strategy on the top drop list. 
Switcher balls made later will have the same behavior as whatever the previously made Switchers have.
Clear button will clear all the balls on canvas